20
00:01:54,735 --> 00:01:56,795
The porridge is too watery.

21
00:01:56,795 --> 00:01:59,155
The kids are growing.

22
00:01:59,155 --> 00:02:01,055
Put more rice into this.

23
00:02:02,134 --> 00:02:05,035
Your Highness, the rice price is on the rise.

24
00:02:05,035 --> 00:02:07,374
Jishan Hall in the capital opened not long ago.

25
00:02:07,375 --> 00:02:11,835
We don't have an abundance of money or rice.

26
00:02:13,935 --> 00:02:16,974
I received a handsome reward at the palace.

27
00:02:16,974 --> 00:02:19,295
We'll put that to use.

28
00:02:19,295 --> 00:02:20,914
Yes.

29
00:02:24,875 --> 00:02:27,334
Is there anything else?

30
00:02:27,334 --> 00:02:30,814
I'm afraid Official Shen won't be here again.

31
00:02:30,815 --> 00:02:34,495
After all, you refused to marry him in front of everyone.

32
00:02:34,495 --> 00:02:38,554
Mr. Shen, what does your name mean?

33
00:02:43,955 --> 00:02:46,394
Jinghong Yipie?

34
00:02:46,394 --> 00:02:49,394
Isn't this your name?

35
00:02:49,394 --> 00:02:52,415
This line is an idiom.

36
00:02:52,415 --> 00:02:57,534
    
 It means a great wonder that is transient

37
00:02:57,534 --> 00:02:59,855
but not easily forgotten.

38
00:02:59,855 --> 00:03:02,114
It stays in your memory.

39
00:03:03,854 --> 00:03:06,193
- Understood? 
 - Yes.

40
00:03:35,134 --> 00:03:36,334
I've been searching all day.

41
00:03:36,335 --> 00:03:38,755
There you are, our Master Scholar.

42
00:03:38,755 --> 00:03:41,155
Time to receive your decree.

43
00:03:41,155 --> 00:03:43,914
The imperial decree arrives!

44
00:03:50,034 --> 00:03:53,094
Shen Jinghong of Huaizhou,

45
00:03:53,094 --> 00:03:56,514
the Master Scholar of the 24th year of the Zhaoming Reign,

46
00:03:56,514 --> 00:03:59,834
will hereby receive the Primary Six-Rank position of editor,

47
00:03:59,834 --> 00:04:02,214
implemented by the head of Hanlin Academy.

48
00:04:02,214 --> 00:04:05,514
The 24th year of the Zhaoming Reign, on the fifth day of the third month.

49
00:04:05,514 --> 00:04:07,534
The end.

50
00:04:07,535 --> 00:04:09,695
I'm grateful to His Majesty.

51
00:04:34,935 --> 00:04:39,915
I am here to congratulate you on winning first place.

52
00:04:39,915 --> 00:04:42,935
I was waiting at your home, but you never showed up.

53
00:04:42,935 --> 00:04:46,574
As it turned out, you're at my sister's place.

54
00:04:46,575 --> 00:04:48,354
My apologies, Your Highness.

55
00:04:48,354 --> 00:04:51,493
Well, I'm not that petty of a person.

56
00:04:51,494 --> 00:04:53,514
Chen'er, it's not Mr. Shen's fault.

57
00:04:53,514 --> 00:04:56,074
He's been helping out at Jishan Hall lately.

58
00:04:56,074 --> 00:04:58,375
The kids love him.

59
00:04:59,694 --> 00:05:01,654
You're kind as ever.

60
00:05:02,575 --> 00:05:06,554
If Jishan Hall needs anything, let me know.

61
00:05:06,575 --> 00:05:09,155
Chen'er, you have my thanks.

62
00:05:09,155 --> 00:05:11,975
Don't mention it, Sister.

63
00:05:11,975 --> 00:05:17,373
I was going to celebrate for you, but it seems you have work at hand.

64
00:05:17,374 --> 00:05:19,094
I appreciate the thought, Your Highness.

65
00:05:19,095 --> 00:05:23,034
However, I promised the children to give them a lesson.

66
00:05:23,034 --> 00:05:25,754
It's all right. We can meet up later.

67
00:05:25,775 --> 00:05:29,234
Sister, I take my leave now.

68
00:05:29,234 --> 00:05:30,795
See His Highness off for me.

69
00:05:30,795 --> 00:05:32,295
Yes.

70
00:05:47,135 --> 00:05:49,774
- Come with me. 
 - Yes.

71
00:05:52,135 --> 00:05:54,754
Becoming the Master Scholar is worth celebrating.

72
00:05:54,754 --> 00:05:57,395
I have a book titled "Records of Governance."

73
00:05:57,395 --> 00:05:59,214
It's my gift to you.

74
00:06:00,235 --> 00:06:02,994
The court is unpredictable. A great duty warrants a long journey.

75
00:06:02,994 --> 00:06:04,954
Do not give up halfway.

76
00:06:04,954 --> 00:06:06,895
I'll remember that.

77
00:06:34,814 --> 00:06:36,613
The First Prince has high expectations of you.

78
00:06:36,614 --> 00:06:38,334
Your career should be your priority.

79
00:06:38,335 --> 00:06:40,175
Do your best as his aide.

80
00:06:40,175 --> 00:06:44,834
Do not waste your time and effort on distractions.

81
00:06:48,095 --> 00:06:52,215
An officer must serve the people.

82
00:06:52,215 --> 00:06:56,775
What I did today is a service for the people.

83
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:08,280
   

84
00:07:24,035 --> 00:07:27,374
Young Lady, everything is packed up.

85
00:07:27,374 --> 00:07:30,614
Housing in Zhuque Street comes with too steep a price.

86
00:07:30,614 --> 00:07:34,614
We barely have money left after we pay the rent.

87
00:07:34,614 --> 00:07:36,714
Don't worry.

88
00:07:36,714 --> 00:07:39,707
I will do my best to make more money.

89
00:07:39,708 --> 00:07:41,308
I won't let you starve.

90
00:07:41,308 --> 00:07:43,314
None of us should starve.

91
00:07:43,314 --> 00:07:46,575
Indeed. No one will be starved.

92
00:07:49,934 --> 00:07:52,915
By the way, Juli, pack these herbs up for me.

93
00:07:52,915 --> 00:07:55,915
Send them to Madam Lu and Miss Song.

94
00:07:55,915 --> 00:07:59,593
After we move to Zhuque Street, we'll live pretty far from Flower Alley.

95
00:07:59,593 --> 00:08:02,675
Commuting won't be as easy as now.

96
00:08:02,675 --> 00:08:05,853
Save the frequently used herbs for them in case of an emergency.

97
00:08:05,854 --> 00:08:07,454
Yes.

